x\ge 2R
 R=\max\left(1,\sum_{k=0}^{2n}|a_k|\right), 
 x≥2R \implies P(x)\ge (2R)^{2n}\cdot R\ge 2^{2n}>0. 
x≤-2R \implies P(x)≤-(2R)^{2n}\cdot R≤-2^{2n}<0.
